    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i don't want to \"carry it forward.\" i don't see the point in carrying anything. every single thing i do is just reminded me that they aren't there. it’s like i’m just a ghost in my own life. if i'm just going to be in pain every single day for the rest of my life... what's the actual purpose of that?",
